Body:
Style scrollbar to match Avengers theme.

**Requirements:**
- ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 12px }
- ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: --dark-bg }
- ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: linear-gradient(--primary-red; --gold); border-radius: 6px }
- ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { filter: brightness(1.2) }
- transition on color change
- Firefox fallback: scrollbar-color and scrollbar-width

**Depends on:** #2 (page content)
